    "Id": "chassisdef_ursus_URS-PR",
    "Name": "Ursus",
    "Details": "The Ursus-PR was created by engineers from Clan Ghost Bear and the Free Rasalhague Republic. The standard weapons were removed and replaced by a pair of ProtoMech AC/8s, an ER Flamer, an Improved Heavy Medium Laser, and a trio of AP Gauss Rifles. The ammunition and gauss weapons are protected by CASE II, while the rest of the armor remains the same. The most interesting part of this refit isn't the weapons, but the Improved C3 Computer installed in the center torso. This allows a Star of Ursus-PRs to exchange targeting data. With its emphasis on anti-infantry weapons and short range combat, the 'Mech is apparently intended for anti-insurgency work.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Distracting</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.1</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Right Lower</color>",
